It's about this piece of code:
```ts
// If response type is defined, only TypedResponse is allowed.
  R extends {
    responses: {
      [statusCode: string]: {
        content: {
          [mediaType: string]: ZodMediaTypeObject
        }
      }
    }
  }
    ? HandlerTypedResponse<OutputType<R>>
    : HandlerAllResponse<OutputType<R>>
```

